<item>
            <title>[DOXIA-760] Clarify default table cell alignment</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DOXIA-760</link>
                <project id="12317230" key="DOXIA">Maven Doxia (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Compare with the discussion at &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MSKINS-230?page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels%3Acomment-tabpanel&amp;amp;focusedCommentId=17897626#comment-17897626&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MSKINS-230?page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels%3Acomment-tabpanel&amp;amp;focusedCommentId=17897626#comment-17897626&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For markdown one needs to leverage &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
:---
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;for left alignment (&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.github.com/gfm/#tables-extension-&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.github.com/gfm/#tables-extension-&lt;/a&gt;) instead of&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
---
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;in the delimiter row. The latter must only be used for default alignment.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
