                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17897688" author="kwin" created="Tue, 12 Nov 2024 18:02:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=michael-o&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;michael-o&quot;&gt;michael-o&lt;/a&gt; How can one now indicate for a two column table a default (whatever that is) alignment for the first column, but aligning the second one centrally with &lt;a href=&quot;https://maven.apache.org/doxia/doxia/doxia-sink-api/apidocs/org/apache/maven/doxia/sink/Sink.html#tableRows-int:A-boolean-&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Sink.tableRows(...)&lt;/a&gt; The only constants defined for the first argument array items is &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://maven.apache.org/doxia/doxia/doxia-sink-api/apidocs/org/apache/maven/doxia/sink/Sink.html#JUSTIFY_LEFT&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maven.apache.org/doxia/doxia/doxia-sink-api/apidocs/org/apache/maven/doxia/sink/Sink.html#JUSTIFY_LEFT&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://maven.apache.org/doxia/doxia/doxia-sink-api/apidocs/org/apache/maven/doxia/sink/Sink.html#JUSTIFY_CENTER&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maven.apache.org/doxia/doxia/doxia-sink-api/apidocs/org/apache/maven/doxia/sink/Sink.html#JUSTIFY_CENTER&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://maven.apache.org/doxia/doxia/doxia-sink-api/apidocs/org/apache/maven/doxia/sink/Sink.html#JUSTIFY_RIGHT&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maven.apache.org/doxia/doxia/doxia-sink-api/apidocs/org/apache/maven/doxia/sink/Sink.html#JUSTIFY_RIGHT&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Should we introduce a 4th choice named &lt;tt&gt;JUSTIFY_DEFAULT&lt;/tt&gt; being -1?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17897696" author="kwin" created="Tue, 12 Nov 2024 18:38:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;APT does not even have a notion for default alignment of tables: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maven.apache.org/doxia/references/apt-format.html#table&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maven.apache.org/doxia/references/apt-format.html#table&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17897851" author="michael-o" created="Wed, 13 Nov 2024 08:27:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We should first change Doxia Sink API...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17897862" author="kwin" created="Wed, 13 Nov 2024 09:07:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I drafted something in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/pull/248&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/pull/248&lt;/a&gt;. Please have a look.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17900185" author="kwin" created="Thu, 21 Nov 2024 21:23:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/commit/c36b51695bdf4fe6f515d7e3fcdcec264867d990&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/commit/c36b51695bdf4fe6f515d7e3fcdcec264867d990&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="18006251" author="sparsick" created="Tue, 15 Jul 2025 10:00:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This project has moved from Jira to GitHub Issues. This issue was migrated to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-doxia/issues/875&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;apache/maven-doxia#875&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
